WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:01.900
Hello, ma'am.

2
00:00:01.900 --> 00:00:03.300
Can you make an appointment?

3
00:00:03.600 --> 00:00:04.866
Stop Chuan to change surname

4
00:00:05.100 --> 00:00:07.300
I just don't want to have anything to do with the Zhao family anymore

5
00:00:07.300 --> 00:00:09.566
If I let everyone know about his relationship with me

6
00:00:09.566 --> 00:00:10.900
It's troublesome

7
00:00:12.100 --> 00:00:15.066
Last time I saw you in business with Mr. Gu

8
00:00:15.533 --> 00:00:17.700
I happened to be working nearby today

9
00:00:17.766 --> 00:00:19.300
Just drop by

10
00:00:19.533 --> 00:00:22.166
Just tell him that Gu Lan is visiting

11
00:00:22.266 --> 00:00:23.300
He knew it.

12
00:00:23.300 --> 00:00:25.066
Ok, wait a minute.

13
00:00:27.933 --> 00:00:28.733
Mr. Gu

14
00:00:32.133 --> 00:00:33.866
Mom, why are you here?

15
00:00:36.466 --> 00:00:37.900
What about the fox spirit?

16
00:00:38.166 --> 00:00:39.066
What do you mean?

17
00:00:39.066 --> 00:00:42.500
I heard you hired a new personal secretary

18
00:00:42.733 --> 00:00:45.100
Come to work covered in hickeys

19
00:00:45.100 --> 00:00:47.100
Also hooked up with you

20
00:00:49.766 --> 00:00:51.200
Really you

21
00:00:51.200 --> 00:00:54.300
I'm telling you, you should fire him for me now

22
00:00:54.333 --> 00:00:57.600
Mom, don't get involved in my company's affairs

23
00:00:57.700 --> 00:00:59.666
Then you still let Tingting come to work?

24
00:00:59.666 --> 00:01:02.266
It can't be the company's business again

25
00:01:02.300 --> 00:01:03.700
I can't care, can I?

26
00:01:03.700 --> 00:01:06.400
Well, I'll take care of your personal affairs

27
00:01:06.466 --> 00:01:08.366
You, quickly give me a divorce

28
00:01:08.366 --> 00:01:09.900
Marry Tingting to me

29
00:01:09.933 --> 00:01:11.100
It's even less likely

30
00:01:11.533 --> 00:01:14.366
My words are not working well now, are they?

31
00:01:15.266 --> 00:01:16.933
Mom, don't you know?

32
00:01:16.933 --> 00:01:19.000
Shen Pinting was late at the company yesterday and committed murder

33
00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:20.266
How is that possible?

34
00:01:20.800 --> 00:01:23.466
He is obviously such a kind and good girl

35
00:01:23.466 --> 00:01:24.266
kind

36
00:01:24.966 --> 00:01:26.566
I haven't had a word with him yet

37
00:01:26.566 --> 00:01:28.200
He dares to use you as a gun

38
00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:29.833
If you marry him like this

39
00:01:29.900 --> 00:01:32.900
Can the Gu family still be at peace? But he is the daughter of the Shen family

40
00:01:33.466 --> 00:01:38.566
Much better than that lowly bitch Yunyao, Mom

41
00:01:38.900 --> 00:01:41.000
Yunyao is still my wife after all

42
00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:43.666
If you scold him, you are scold me.

43
00:01:43.666 --> 00:01:46.866
So I told you to divorce him quickly

